          <div style="display:inline-block; background:#FEF3C7; color:#92400E; font-size:.72rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; padding:.3rem 1rem; border-radius:50px; margin-bottom:.6rem;">ימי הולדת</div>
